baseline_texts: This frame shows a close-up view of a clear plastic cup placed inside a sink. Water is being poured into the cup from above, causing bubbles and some splashing. The cup is situated on a textured surface, likely a drying mat or a sink liner. The lighting is warm and reflects off the metal surface of the sink. On the right side of the frame, part of a pot or pan with condensation on its inside surface is visible.

This frame shows a close-up view of a clear plastic cup placed in a sink. Water is being poured or flowing into the cup from above. The cup is sitting on a textured mat inside the sink. To the right side of the frame, part of a dark-colored, rounded object is visible, possibly a bowl or a pot. The lighting suggests the image was taken indoors, with some reflections visible on the metallic surface of the sink.
